1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 6=

11
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:05,120
Who are you?

12
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:06,439
Immortal King.

13
00:01:06,439 --> 00:01:09,640
Once I come out of seclusion,
I'll settle the score with you.

14
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:13,519
I'll take your soul and complete
the Demon Clan's grand plan.

15
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:14,760
Too noisy.

16
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:22,079
Wubing, did he hurt you?

17
00:01:22,079 --> 00:01:22,840
Are you okay?

18
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:25,000
I'm fine. Don't worry.

19
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,359
Su Wubing,

20
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:28,480
why were you pretending
to be weak before?

21
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:29,719
Now you're this strong.

22
00:01:30,879 --> 00:01:32,799
Are you getting close to Ningxue

23
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:33,840
to protect her,

24
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:34,840
or do you have other motives?

25
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:37,760
Don't tell her what just happened.

26
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:40,079
Why keep me in the dark?

27
00:01:40,879 --> 00:01:42,239
What are you hiding from me?

28
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:44,680
(The demons have already shown up.)

29
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:46,120
(If they can find me,)

30
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,680
(they can find Ningxue too.)

31
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:49,680
Ningxue...

32
00:01:50,599 --> 00:01:52,040
He's not just trying to win you over;

33
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,760
he's also got a good "little sister".

34
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:59,000
I'm not feeling well. I want to go home.

35
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:01,840
Yingying, he treats Tian
like a real sister.

36
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,640
You know her?

37
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:05,480
Ningxue.

38
00:02:07,239 --> 00:02:08,879
Tian just got scared.

39
00:02:09,199 --> 00:02:10,080
Take her home first.

40
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,960
I'll explain everything to Yingying

41
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,159
and come find you.

42
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:25,840
Why didn't you let me
tell Ningxue just now?

43
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:26,960
And...

44
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:29,039
why were you acting weak
at the martial hall?

45
00:02:30,080 --> 00:02:32,680
And now you're staying at the Lin family
under the excuse of protecting her.

46
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,520
What's your real goal?

47
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,039
I just don't want her living in fear.

48
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:40,080
That's why I didn't tell her.

49
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,240
As for the rest...

50
00:02:44,319 --> 00:02:45,199
I'll explain another day.

51
00:02:45,639 --> 00:02:46,840
No. Tell me now.

52
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,240
What's wrong with you?

53
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,639
I barely even used force.

54
00:02:56,039 --> 00:02:58,439
Ye Tianmiao's Herb Order...

55
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:01,080
How do you have this?

56
00:03:02,759 --> 00:03:03,879
Take me to the Herbal Hall.

57
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:05,520
Now.

58
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:21,680
So you're Su Wubing's sister?

59
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,439
We are...

60
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:25,000
Childhood sweethearts?

61
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:31,639
Ningxue, do you... like Wubing?

62
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,360
You're overthinking it.

63
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,960
He saved my father.

64
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,360
I'm just repaying a debt.

65
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,120
That's all.

66
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,840
So the house we're living in is yours?

67
00:03:43,439 --> 00:03:44,879
I gave it to him.

68
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:46,159
I'm not taking it back.

69
00:03:48,039 --> 00:03:51,479
(She clearly likes him
and she's so generous...)

70
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:52,759
(How am I supposed to compete?)

71
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,599
(Childhood sweethearts...)

72
00:03:58,639 --> 00:04:00,479
(Looks like he really cares about her.)

73
00:04:08,879 --> 00:04:09,319
Stop!

74
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,400
Who are you?

75
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:13,599
I'm from Shan family. Move aside!

76
00:04:14,439 --> 00:04:15,919
Another one here to
curry favor for pills?

77
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:16,519
Get lost!

78
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,120
You...

79
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:25,680
This...

80
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,040
Please come in.

81
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,480
What's going on?

82
00:04:32,959 --> 00:04:33,800
Without Master's order,

83
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,759
no entry for outsiders.

84
00:04:35,079 --> 00:04:35,519
You.

85
00:04:45,079 --> 00:04:46,519
Look at him.

86
00:04:46,959 --> 00:04:48,439
He was unstoppable just now,

87
00:04:48,439 --> 00:04:49,680
and now he's this weak?

88
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:51,959
And he even has the Herb Token...

89
00:04:53,319 --> 00:04:55,120
Just how many secrets is he hiding?

90
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,600
And Ningxue and him...

91
00:05:10,839 --> 00:05:11,639
Tianmiao.

92
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,480
My Lord.

93
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:23,600
Your mortal body can't

94
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:26,560
withstand Heavenly God Realm power.

95
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:30,560
Every time you use immortal energy,
it damages your meridians.

96
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,079
This body still

97
00:05:33,439 --> 00:05:34,600
hasn't adapted.

98
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:36,519
Someone.

99
00:05:38,319 --> 00:05:39,519
Help my Lord change.

100
00:05:39,759 --> 00:05:40,519
Yes.

101
00:06:04,759 --> 00:06:05,959
(This medicinal pool is)

102
00:06:05,959 --> 00:06:08,879
(filled with rare treasures
collected by me.)

103
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:12,199
(It will greatly help restore
your cultivation.)

104
00:06:17,719 --> 00:06:20,007
(Herbal Hall)

105
00:06:44,279 --> 00:06:45,399
(Su Wubing...?)

106
00:06:45,639 --> 00:06:46,720
(How is he here?)

107
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:53,079
(I didn't expect his physique
to be this good.)

108
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:12,120
Dr. Ye...

109
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:16,040
Su Wubing...

110
00:07:21,879 --> 00:07:23,759
(She actually has a pure Yin body.)

111
00:07:41,079 --> 00:07:43,480
(It forms at the peak of extreme Yin,)

112
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:45,279
(absorbing innate Yin energy.)

113
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,079
(The poison seeps into bones.)

114
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:49,480
(When it flares up,
it's agony beyond words.)

115
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,319
Sorry for this.

116
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,279
Dr. Ye.

117
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,480
I know you can hear me.

118
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,399
Your condition is special.

119
00:08:07,519 --> 00:08:08,800
If I don't treat you in time,

120
00:08:09,199 --> 00:08:10,000
I'm afraid you...

121
00:08:40,143 --> 00:08:44,246
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

122
00:08:44,246 --> 00:08:48,966
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

123
00:08:48,966 --> 00:08:53,846
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

124
00:08:53,846 --> 00:08:58,966
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

125
00:08:58,966 --> 00:09:03,366
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

126
00:09:03,366 --> 00:09:08,046
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

127
00:09:08,046 --> 00:09:13,446
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

128
00:09:13,446 --> 00:09:19,840
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

